name: Sole-Protector Exclusive Dealer
description:
Sole-Protector™ is made by 3M™, they use a Resin based technology to produce this ultra clear ultra strong urethane.

This is not over the counter type film, this is a commercial grade high quality proprietary film for SP. When applying you can pull and stretch the film for perfect fitment, I've even seen some professional installation done with a blow drier for a super snug fit ( not required ) not only is it great when it comes to keeping lighter colored soles clean , it will also save from obvious situations like gum, crap, car fluids, etc.

Another huge benefit of the SP is that after you rocked your shoe's casually 40+ times you can peel off the SP and have fresh, DS soles with 100% traction to play ball in. The film is paint friendly and will always come off in one piece without leaving a trace of residue; we can thank the team of scientist over at 3M ™ labs for that! 

Price is for a set of 2 SPs and including shipping. 
**PLEASE ADVISE YOUR SHOE SIZE DURING CHECK OUT**
